Package: disclosuR
Type: Package
Title: Text conversion from NexisUni PDFs to R data frames
Version: 0.0.1.0
Date: 2023-04-19
Author: Jonas Roettger
Maintainer: Jonas Roettger <jonas.roettger@gmx.net>
Description: This package contains functions to transform newswire and earnings calls transcript from PDF to R data frames. Various newswires and FairDisclosure earnings calls format are supported (all otainable from NexisUni). 
Imports: dplyr, lubridate, pdftools, Qdap, SentimentAnalysis, stringi, stringr, syuzhet, zoo
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
